  "description": "A close-up photograph of a vibrant, orange-red flower in bloom. The flower is shaped somewhat like a trumpet or a bird's beak, with gently curving petals.  The interior of the flower reveals a delicate, pale yellow structure, possibly the stamen or pistil.  The flower appears to be in soft focus, with a shallow depth of field that blurs the background into a dark, muted tone. The lighting highlights the texture of the petals and adds dimension to the bloom. The flower's orientation is slightly angled downwards. The backdrop is a dark, out-of-focus green.",
